        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer753350306" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14488959982544489511">The sole reason I gave this a 4 stars was because now this series is finally over. And the ending was the EXACT SAME THING!</span>

